    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a baking tray (or two!) with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> and cut into 1 rectangle per person</p><p>Spoon the <strong>samosa filling</strong> down the middle of each pastry rectangle and brush a little <strong>cold water </strong>around the edges</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1690206408414-x200.jpg",
