        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fold your pastry over the filling and seal firmly together, then use a fork to crimp along the edge</p><p>Roll the <strong>sealed pastries</strong>, starting at one end, into a spiral</p><p>Transfer the <strong>pastry spirals</strong> to the lined baking tray[s] and put the tray[s] in the oven for 22-25 min or until golden and crisp – these are your <strong>vegetable samosa pinwheels</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
