      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>chutney</strong> with the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>mint & coriander chutney yoghurt</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>baby leaf salad</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>remaining cider vinegar </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and toss – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
