    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, spread the <strong>mango chutney </strong>over the <strong>vegetable samosa pinwheels</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>glazed vegetable samosa pinwheels</strong> with the <strong>nigella wedges</strong>, <strong>dressed salad</strong> and <strong>mint & coriander chutney yoghurt</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
